name: Chicken Tagine Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Combine spices and rub into chicken pieces. Heat oil in a frying pan, add garlic and chicken and cook until golden. Transfer to a casserole dish with remaining spices, tomatoes, stock, tomato paste and honey.
Meanwhile, cut vegetables into chunks. Stir into casserole with dates.
Cover with lid and bake for about 1 hour or until meat and vegetables are tender.
Meanwhile, place couscous in a heatproof bowl. Add 2 cups boiling water. Cover and stand for 5 minutes. Stir with a fork to separate couscous grains. Season. Serve tagine with couscous.
